### Get all cases
GET http://localhost:3000/cases

### Get user balance (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:3000/users/balance
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Open a case (requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:3000/cases/open
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "caseUuid": "CASE_UUID_HERE"
}

### Create a case (requires admin rights)
POST http://localhost:3000/cases/create
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Test Case",
    "description": "A test case for development",
    "price": 15.00,
    "rarity": "RARE",
    "possibleCards": ["Test Card 1", "Test Card 2", "Test Card 3"],
    "cardWeights": [50, 30, 20]
}
